              "id": "4jbTb",
              "name": "s13ct",
              "fill": "$textSecondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Add Card — Opens modal form with all fields\nBatch Import — CSV upload with column mapping UI\nBatch Export — Downloads filtered results as CSV\nDelete Selected — Multi-select via checkboxes, confirm dialog\nEdit — Click row to open edit modal (same as Add form)\nValidation: required fields, year range, price >= 0\nCascade check: deleting player warns about orphaned cards",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 11,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        }
