              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Missing Prices — WHERE currentPrice IS NULL\nPrice Anomalies — ABS(price_change_pct) > 200 in 24h\nMissing Images — WHERE imageURL IS NULL OR imageURL = ''\nOrphaned Players — players LEFT JOIN cards WHERE card IS NULL\nStale Summaries — WHERE updated_at < now() - 7 days\nPlayer-Card Orphans — cards WHERE player_id NOT IN players",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 11,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
