              "fill": "$textSecondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Score = 100 - (weighted_issue_count)\nWeights: Missing Price=0.5, Price Anomaly=1.0\nMissing Image=0.3, Orphans=2.0, Stale=0.2\nThresholds: >90 Excellent, >70 Good, >50 Fair, <50 Poor\nColor: Green >70, Yellow 50-70, Red <50",
