              "fill": "$textSecondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "1. Impression — paywall_shown event fired\n2. CTA Click — user taps Subscribe/Continue button\n3. Subscribe — StoreKit purchase completed\n4. Active (30d) — user still active 30 days post-sub\nDrop-off calculated between each step\nAll events tracked via AnalyticsService",
