              "content": "Source — PaywallSource enum dropdown\nVariant — PaywallVariant (soft/hard) dropdown\nPlan — SubscriptionTier filter (monthly/yearly/lifetime)\nTime Range — Date picker, default 30 days\nAll filters apply to funnel + table + chart simultaneously\nDrill-down: click funnel step to see user list",
